          Frequently asked questions on Electric

          Which are the expensive Electric cars in India?

          The most expensive Electric cars in India are Spectre, Eletre, AMG EQS, i7, RS e-tron GT.

          The lowest priced Electric cars in India are R3, EaS E, Comet EV, Tiago EV, Punch EV.
